Aubameyang on why didn&rsquo;t take the 2nd penalty.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I know that Laca is back and I scored twice, I think it's good for his confidence and that's why.&rdquo;

Rob Holding on Lehmann: &ldquo;Jens has been a big difference since he&rsquo;s come in. He&rsquo;s very demanding &amp; not afraid to get down &amp; dirty with you. He&rsquo;ll get at you &amp; I&rsquo;ll have a little snap back, but then after training we&rsquo;ll speak about it &amp; come to an agreement on what went on.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Holding on Lehmann: &ldquo;Then, the next day, it&rsquo;s like nothing happened. There&rsquo;s no grudges held &amp; it&rsquo;s what I think is key to getting the best out of me. You&rsquo;re more aggressive &amp; more demanding as a consequence &amp; that&rsquo;s what I need to be as a centre-half.&rdquo;
